<p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240512/1715496771777057398.png" title="1715496771777057398.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-12 145152.png" width="950" height="584" style="width: 950px; height: 584px;"/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 30.9999px;">为深入学习贯彻习近平总书记关于党纪学习教育的重要讲话和重要指示精神，提高党员的政治觉悟和纪律意识，进一步加强年轻干部的纪律意识和素质提升，</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; line-height: 1.93em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">经济管理学院领导班子于2024年4月30日在A10-314组织开展党纪学习教育集中学习研讨。本次集中学习由党总支书记蔡平主持，院长韩士专、常务副院长颜小燕出席。</span></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; line-height: 1.93em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240512/1715496890122063947.png" title="1715496890122063947.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-12 145443.png" width="969" height="505" style="width: 969px; height: 505px;"/></span></p><p style="white-space: normal; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-indent: 2.21428em; caret-color: red; line-height: 1.93em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">本次集中学习主要围绕《中国共产党纪律处分条例》(以下简称《条例》)第四章原文和对年轻干部开展纪律教育。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">会议首先由蔡平书记逐章逐条领学《条例》第四章原文，并对学习内容进行了深入解读。他指出党员干部要遵纪守法，守好纪法红线、坚守清廉底线，自觉履行好全面从严治党的政治责任，以上率下形成“头雁效应”，以“关键少数”带动“绝大多数”，一级带一级、一级抓一级，积极营造风清气正的良好政治生态。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">随后，会议上通过案例分析、互动讨论的形式对年轻干部开展纪律教育，引导年轻干部们深入了解对违法犯罪党员的纪律处分的重要性和必要性，教育年轻干部树立正确的权力观、政绩观、事业观，始终做到忠诚干净担当。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">最后，蔡平书记对年轻干部提出以下几点要求:一是严格遵守党纪规定，要时刻绷紧党纪这根弦，自觉遵守党的各项规定和纪律;二是强化廉洁自律意识，自觉抵制各种形式的腐败和不正之风;三是加强学习提升素质，提高政治觉悟和业务水平，不断提升自身素质，为更好地履行党员干部的职责作出积极贡献。</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-align: center; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240512/1715497066312099475.png" title="1715497066312099475.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-05-12 145454.png" width="982" height="469" style="width: 982px; height: 469px;"/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="text-indent: 30.9999px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">通过本次党纪学习教育，有利于加强党员干部的党性教育、规范党员行为，同时对各党员干部起到警示作用，要进一步提高政治站位，自觉做到言行一致，秉承务实创新的工作作风，更好地履行党员的职责和使命，为学院及学校的的蓬勃发展贡献自己的力量。</span></p>